definitions.definition: Of or pertaining to, or affected by, rickets ( “ a disorder of infancy and early childhood due to a deficiency of vitamin D , causing soft or weak bones ” ) .
In a precarious or weak condition ; likely to break down or collapse ; feeble , rickety .

main_definition: ( pathology ) Of or pertaining to, or affected by, rickets ( “ a disorder of infancy and early childhood due to a deficiency of vitamin D , causing soft or weak bones ” ) . [from 18th c.]
secondary_definitions: ( figurative ) In a precarious or weak condition ; likely to break down or collapse ; feeble , rickety . [from 19th c.]
